# Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.

# --- Analytics (optional) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# --- OpenSky Network API (optional but recommended) ---
# Register at https://opensky-network.org/register to get free credentials
# Authenticated users get 5x more API credits (20 vs 4 per minute)
# This enables wider coverage and better data availability
# OPENSKY_USERNAME=your_username_here
# OPENSKY_PASSWORD=your_password_here

# --- Notes ---
# OpenSky API calls are made directly from the browser (CORS supported).
# No server-side credentials are needed for basic usage.
# Add credentials above to increase data availability and global coverage.
